up his strengths and learned to manage his weaknesses, patiently waited for=
 his enemies to eliminate themselves, and came to represent what Rome stood=
 for in the eyes of the Roman people. He built up his capabilities to match=
 his ambitions.&#160;</p><div class=3D"captioned-image-container-static" st=
